Preheat the oven to 160C/140C Fan/Gas 2.Stir all of the ingredients, except the jam, together in a large bowl. pour the mixture into the baking dishes.Cover the dishes with a lid or sheet of aluminium foil and cook in the oven for 1Â½ hours. Remove the lid or foil and cook for a further 20 minutes, or until the rice is tender and the top is lightly golden and has formed a skin.Spoon the rice pudding into serving bowls and serve with spoonfuls of jam.